title: Garth Ennis: The Pro (2002/2012) (Digital-GN-1280|Fawkes-Empire)

Overview:  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Pro_%28comics%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Pro_%28comics%29</a>




Contains:   The Pro (2002) (Digital GN - 2012 Edition) (Fawkes-Empire)


            (edition includes a bonus short story, "The Pro Meets the Ho") 


             " The Pro is laughing with me, not at me. Well, 
               okay, it's doing both. But it's still great. "    - Mark Waid

             " This is the comic that Garth, Amanda and
               Jimmy will be apologizing for in Heaven
               minutes before being sent directly to
               Hell. But hey, if their eternal damnation
               is the only downside, then I demand a sequel. "   - Gail Simone

             " Amanda Conner is hot. "                           - Joe Casey

             " This is the WATCHMEN of comics
               about unprotected sex with whores. "              - Brian K Vaughan

             " Joe Casey is a dead man. "                        - Jimmy Palmiotti

            (as quoted on the back cover)
